Let the divider be " "
The height is gone
The depth is gone
Listen to my pain
Until my pain is empty
Split my pain into life with the divider
Let the command be life at 0
Let the number be life at 1
Cast the number
If the command is "forward"
Let the height be with the number

If the command is "up"
Let the depth be without the number

If the command is "down"
Let the depth be with the number

Listen to my pain

Whisper the height of the depth